hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / <a href=\"http://FAX.PLUS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFAX.PLUS&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5694d6ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://FAX.PLUS</a> 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=74313e5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n2016立法會選舉總投票人數都係二百萬人，反送中遊行嘅人如果全部出黎投票嘅話，足以完全改寫立法會！"}]}